                break;

            default :
              {
                Cerr << "Default case..." << finl;
                Cerr << "Les mots cles possibles sont "<< les_mots <<" { et }" << finl;
                Cerr << "Vous avez lu :" << motlu << finl;
                break;
              }
            }
          is >> motlu;
        }
      is >> motlu;
      if (motlu != accfermee)
        {
          Cerr << "Error while reading in Traitement_particulier_NS_canal" << finl;;
          Cerr << "We were expecting a }" << finl;
          exit();
        }
    }
  else
    {
      Cerr << "Error while reading in Traitement_particulier_NS_canal" << finl;
      Cerr << "We were expecting a {" << finl;
      exit();
    }
